# Persistence boundary -- anything that imports aiosqlite / psycopg / sqlite3
# or ships raw SQL must go through ``src/synthorg/persistence/``. The rules
# below give the persistence layer and its enforcement machinery explicit
# review guardrails per issue #1457's acceptance checklist, even while the
# project is single-maintainer.
src/synthorg/persistence/           @Aureliolo
src/synthorg/**/*sqlite*            @Aureliolo
src/synthorg/**/*postgres*          @Aureliolo
scripts/check_persistence_boundary.py @Aureliolo
docs/design/persistence.md          @Aureliolo
docs/guides/persistence-migrations.md @Aureliolo
